name: YQ_CommercialPedestrain
description:
YQ_CommercialPedestrain

This CKPT is trained because of a quick project test which has a commercial pedestrain in it, time was very limited, so it's not that really powerful kind, but still interesting, and might be helpful if you are working on commercial projects.

(plz download the posts for more info about prompts. It seem I put a lots of wrong information into the neg prompts by a mistake....but still, the img is there anyway...)

below are without control net.

below are with control net.(0.65 of depth, just for stablising the space structure.)
